original_title: Sean's World TV - Hunting Nessie (GONE WRONG)
overview: On the 18th August 2019, YouTuber 'Sean's World TV' was reported missing near Loch Ness.  His whereabouts are still unknown.  Footage unearthed from Sean's phone is currently all that remains.
title: Sean's World TV - Hunting Nessie (GONE WRONG)
